Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[alarm blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone. Shiniga--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,RENEWAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Now, try to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Although this was announced\Nas a worldwide broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth is, we are only broadcasting\Nin the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In actuality, the first of your victims\Nwas a suspect in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, his crime\Nwas only ever reported inside of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] The suspect is now dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I used that information\Nto deduce this much:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and your first victim\Nwas little more than an experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which means that you haven’t been killing\Nfor very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA TASK FORCE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira has found a way to obtain information\Nfrom the task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 141 people in the police force
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,who have access to classified information\Nregarding the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that somewhere in this list\Nof police officers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people closest to them…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we will find our suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SOICHIRO YAGAMI (48) DOB 7/12/59\NDETECTIVE SUPERINTENDENT,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI INVESTIGATION OF THOSE INVOLVED\NWITH THE JAPANESE POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On December 14,\Ntwelve FBI investigators enter Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are on December 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Using prison inmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira conducts experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,manipulating his victims' actions\Nbefore they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He needed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,how much control\Nhe had over his victims
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,before he could use it\Nagainst the 12 agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect Kira had to be one of the people\Nbeing investigated by the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,between the 14th and the 19th of December.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-In fact, I have no doubt.\N-[man groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,AN IMPORTANT WITNESS\NNAOMI MISORA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber's fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi Misora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She was working under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she must have come to Japan\Nwith her fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she was seen with Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible\Nthat she may have found a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,did Kira manage to get to her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Everyone, at this point\NI'd like to focus our investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on only those people\Nwho Raye Penber was tailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Director Kitamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as Detective Superintendent Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, I'd like to place wiretaps\Nand surveillance cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in both households.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my son you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you honestly telling me\Nthat you suspect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,CONTACT WITH LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Relax, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's true that Kira hates losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also true that most people\Nwould rather win than lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that. He's going for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that you, Light Yagami,\Nare in fact Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] You think I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuga,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what would it take to get you\Nto believe that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, isn't there something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that truth will be revealed.\NJust let things run their course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA MURDERS\NUSING A TELEVISION STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,MESSAGE FROM KIRA\N4 VIDEOS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[director] Our audience rating\Nshould go up 60,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,no, more like 70 percent\Nafter this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[newscaster] It contained a prediction\Nof two deaths, proving that he is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand that the 2nd tape contains\Na message to all people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The news anchor, Mr. Kazuhiko Hibima,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,will die of a heart attack\Nat exactly six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-[heart beating loudly]\N-[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You told us that Kira\Ncouldn't kill without a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] But from what we've just seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's not entirely impossible\Nthat Kira can kill with only a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police!\NStop this broadcast now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] There's a strong possibility\Nthat this Kira is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we should think of him\Nmore as a Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like your permission to ask your son\Nto cooperate with us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI IS SUMMONED\NTO TASK FORCE HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I'd say\Nthis isn't the Kira we are familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's almost exactly\Nhow L, I mean Ryuzaki, said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kira] When we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we can confirm our identities\Nby showing our Shinigami to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If there's a message here\Nwritten in some code that only people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who have this Shinigami power\Ncan understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,there'd be no way for me to decipher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it would only make sense for us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to look into all of the places\Nthat were mentioned in the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When you two are working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to keep a close eye on Light\Nthe entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a slim chance,\Nbut if Light is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's still a possibility\Nthat the Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,may try to contact him somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Mr. Yagami, please ask Mr. Mogi\Nto start following Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can keep tabs\Non what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA AMANE ARRESTED UNDER SUSPICION\NOF BEING THE SECOND KIRA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there. I'm Light's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa Amane. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm Hideki Ryuga.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideki Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I'm not exactly sure\Nhow you will take this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but regarding Misa Amane,\Nthere's something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken her into custody\Nunder suspicion of being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We gathered physical evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from the envelopes\Nsent by the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, hairs and fibers\Ncaught in the masking tape
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,used to seal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They matched what we found in Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA AMANE'S CONFINEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Ryuzaki!\NWhat's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to, you could kill me\Nright, now, couldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Does that mean\Nyou admit to being the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is this the reason you wish to die?\N-[Misa] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I don't know anything\Nabout the Second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI IS CONFINED\NAT HIS OWN REQUEST
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, like I said over the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Why come here to announce\Nthat you could be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an act.\NThere's no "could be" about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light, are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I know I must look\Npretty bad in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with this useless pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize I was the one\Npushing for confinement,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I asked you to put me in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But this whole thing\Nis completely pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks’ worth of criminals\Nwere just murdered all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA RETURNS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO PEOPLE RELEASED
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I'm not sure how much more of this\Nthe three of them can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, you have no reason\Nto keep Light locked up anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been fifty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you here\Nand then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's crazy!\N-Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop, Dad. I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-From one murderer to another...\N-No, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] It was\Na convincing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As we discussed,\NI will end their confinement immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI IS SUMMONED AGAIN\NTO HELP WITH THE INVESTIGATION
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you part in this agreement, Light,\Nyou and I will be together 24-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it will be\Nuntil we have brought Kira to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,YOTSUBA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Their deaths have all worked\Nin Yotsuba's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there've been 13 similar deaths\Nin the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,INVESTIGATION AND INFILTRATION\NOF YOTSUBA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Is Kira someone from Yotsuba?\NOr is Kira simply using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'll proceed under the assumption\Nthat this is Kira's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We will focus on Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be sure not to act impulsively,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,out of panic or haste,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't take matters\Ninto your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Taro Matsui.\NI'm an agent with Yoshida Productions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in using Misa Amane\Nas your new spokesperson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, are you watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The eight men who came here\Nwere having a meeting to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-who'd they get Kira to kill for them.\N-[L] If Matsuda dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,our suspicions about the Yotsuba group\Nwould be confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Do you think there’s anything\NI can do to save myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Matsuda, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,KYOSUKE HIGUCHI CONFIRMED AS KIRA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here ready to celebrate\Nwhen they decide to hire you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been my dream\Nto become Kira's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-I know he'll need me by his side.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I happen to be Kira,\Ndoes that mean you'll marry me, Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, based on what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi is Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,THE PLAN TO CAPTURE HIGUCHI\NIS SET IN MOTION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] So, what are you gonna do?\N-[L] I'm going to trick Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-using Sakura TV.\N-Like a hidden camera show!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, we've got a problem.\NTurn on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 1] So, you're saying\None of those people is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 2]Yes. I've got a lot of evidence\Nto prove it, too. [yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] It-- It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see Higuchi. I'm in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You in the red car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull over to the side of the road. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Rem. Let's make the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You were speeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,License, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[officer 1] Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[officer 2] Higuchi ditched the cop\NHe's driving away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is traffic control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[heartbeat]\N-[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! It's too dangerous\Nto allow further action by Higuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he has the same powers\Nas the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He is able to kill\Njust by looking at someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, keep this in mind\Nwhen you move in to arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-[tires screeching]\N-[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!\NStay back or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-I swear! [yells]\N-[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,HIGUCHI'S CAPTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Higuchi, how were you able\Nto kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't believe me,\Nbut I've got a special notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I write someone's name in it\Nwhile thinking of their face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that person dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It was in one of the compartments\Nof Higuchi's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] What' is it, Mr. Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shinigami…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There have to be two notebooks!\NPossibly more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DEATH NOTE AND AN INQUIRY\NINTO ITS RULES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] "How to use it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It says: "The human whose name is written\Nin this notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,shall die."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, there's this last rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this,\N"If the person using the note
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,fails to consecutively write names\Nof people to be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-within 13 days of each other..."\N-[L] ...within 13 days of each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami and Misa Amane\Nare both still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The following is the record,\Nwhich contains everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have investigated on the Kira Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that now you are reading\Nthis message,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,means I am no longer alive at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby leave this record\Nas my firm achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[continuous beep]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] It's been ten days\Nsince Ryuzaki's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we\Nare not gonna die after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We know Watari's true identity now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but we never found out\Nanything about who Ryuzaki really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have guessed that Watari\Nwas actually a famous inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The paper says he founded orphanages\Naround the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,using the fortune\Nhe inherited from his patents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] He was a fine man. A hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't help us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't continue investigating\Nusing this place as our base
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with L and Watari gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm. Light, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to transfer the system\Nand most of the information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,out of here by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel as if I'm stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've created a voice filter\Nidentical to the one Ryuzaki used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can use it\Nto make the police think he is still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and give them orders\Nlike we've doing so far, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to take the place of L?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where he will work from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do we do with the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NWhat are you talking about, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\Nwho can take on the role of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki was killed by Kira\Nbecause he challenged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something I'm eager to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I would be fooling\Nthe people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're really the only one of us\Nwho can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NEven Ryuzaki said so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be capable of succeeding L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun without Ryuzaki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I won't be like Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take big risks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,like challenging Kira directly\Nto gather clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's probably better\Nif we play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki may have been\Na little too confrontational.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to do the same sort of work,\Nusing both this computer and my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be possible for me to act as L\Nin the comfort of my own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be Watari as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be difficult to pull off\Nwith Mum and Sayu around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Things would be easier\Nif I could rent a one-bedroom apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, considering your age,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it certainly wouldn't look odd to anyone\Nif I let you move out on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, yeah! And then we'll be able\Nto use Light's new apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as our taskforce headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's a great idea!\N-[Yagami] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left to figure out now\Nis what to do with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's really not that difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's five of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know none of us\Nwill ever use the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have one of us take it\Nand hide it somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,where no one else can ever get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Chief, it's gotta be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Chief! We can count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a pillar of justice, after all.\N[nervous laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll avenge Ryuzaki together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kira's still out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll catch him. That's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mm-hmm.\N-Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Well then, why don't we\Nhave a little party
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate Light becoming\NL number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Quit fooling around.\NNow's not the time for stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Let's take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our first date in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you enjoy yourself a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Misa…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's move in together.\N-[Misa gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah. I've already rented a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] Yay! Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuk] Victory?\N-[Misa] Over Kiyomi and Mari and Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right, now. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were\Njust using those other girls to trick L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any reason\Nto see them anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Now that L's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean\Nyou've finally settled the score with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in that case, I guess things\Nare gonna get pretty boring from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's not true, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the creation\Nof the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[lightning crackles]
